----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSpinButton.UpGlyph
Summary
  Specifies the bitmap that appears on the up spin button.
Description
  Set UpGlyph to a bitmap object that contains the image that should appear on the face of the up spin
  button. Bring up the Open dialog box from the Object Inspector to choose a bitmap file (with a .BMP
  extension), or specify a bitmap file at runtime.

  If UpGlyph is not assigned then the default up button glyph is used.
See Also
  TJvSpinButton.DownGlyph

